summary: This is a photo sheet and incident report from the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York documenting a possible suicide attempt by inmate Jeffrey Epstein on July 23, 2019. It records the time of the incident and the subsequent photograph taken by a lieutenant.

persons.name: Jeffrey Epstein
persons.context: The inmate who is the subject of the incident report for a possible suicide attempt at the Metropolitan Correctional Center.

events.title: Possible Suicide Attempt by Jeffrey Epstein
events.description: A possible suicide attempt by inmate Jeffrey Epstein was reported at the Metropolitan Correctional Center's Special Housing Unit at 1:27 AM.

locations: Metropolitan Correctional Center, New York, N.Y.
keyFacts: The document records a possible suicide attempt by Jeffrey Epstein on July 23, 2019, at 1:27 AM.
The incident occurred in the Special Housing Unit of the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York.
Photographs of the incident were taken by a lieutenant at 1:55 AM on the same date.
Jeffrey Epstein's inmate register number is listed as #76318-054.
